getAllPSDEFDTColumns.name: UNCLOSEDBUGCNT
getAllPSDEFDTColumns.queryCodeExp: (SELECT COUNT(1) FROM ZT_BUG WHERE PROJECT = t1.`ID` AND `STATUS` <> 'closed' AND DELETED = '0')

getAllPSDEFDTColumns.name: YESTERDAYCTASKCNT
getAllPSDEFDTColumns.queryCodeExp: (select COUNT(1) from zt_task t where t.deleted = '0' and t.project = t1.id and t.`status` = 'closed' and t.closedDate BETWEEN CONCAT(YEAR(DATE_ADD(now(),INTERVAL -1 day)),'-',month(DATE_ADD(now(),INTERVAL -1 day)),'-',day(DATE_ADD(now(),INTERVAL -1 day)),' 00:00:00') and CONCAT(YEAR(DATE_ADD(now(),INTERVAL -1 day)),'-',month(DATE_ADD(now(),INTERVAL -1 day)),'-',day(DATE_ADD(now(),INTERVAL -1 day)),' 23:59:59') )

getAllPSDEFDTColumns.name: UNCONFIRMEDBUGCNT
getAllPSDEFDTColumns.queryCodeExp: (SELECT COUNT(1) FROM ZT_BUG WHERE PROJECT = t1.`ID` AND `CONFIRMED` = 0 AND DELETED = '0')

getAllPSDEFDTColumns.name: FINISHTASKCNT
getAllPSDEFDTColumns.queryCodeExp: (SELECT COUNT(1) FROM ZT_TASK WHERE PROJECT = t1.`ID` AND `STATUS` IN ('done','cancel','closed') AND DELETED = '0')

getAllPSDEFDTColumns.name: TOTALCONSUMED
getAllPSDEFDTColumns.queryCodeExp: (SELECT round(SUM(CONSUMED),0) FROM ZT_TASK WHERE PROJECT = t1.`ID` AND DELETED = '0' AND ( `parent` = '' or `parent` = '0' or `parent` = '-1'))

getAllPSDEFDTColumns.name: RELEASEDSTORYCNT
getAllPSDEFDTColumns.queryCodeExp: (SELECT COUNT(1) FROM ZT_STORY LEFT JOIN ZT_PROJECTSTORY ON ZT_STORY.ID = ZT_PROJECTSTORY.STORY WHERE stage = 'released' AND PROJECT = t1.id AND DELETED = '0')

getAllPSDEFDTColumns.name: CLOSEDSTORYCNT
getAllPSDEFDTColumns.queryCodeExp: (SELECT COUNT(1) FROM ZT_STORY WHERE `STATUS` =  'closed' AND FIND_IN_SET (PRODUCT, (SELECT GROUP_CONCAT(PRODUCT) FROM ZT_PROJECTPRODUCT WHERE PROJECT= t1.`ID`)) AND DELETED = '0' )

getAllPSDEFDTColumns.name: FINISHBUGCNT
getAllPSDEFDTColumns.queryCodeExp: (SELECT COUNT(1) FROM ZT_BUG WHERE PROJECT = t1.`ID` AND `STATUS` <> 'active' AND DELETED = '0')
